Package: rpa4all-vpn
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: wireguard-tools, network-manager, curl
Recommends: resolvconf
Maintainer: Eddie Auto-Dev <edenilson.paschoa@rpa4all.com>
Description: RPA4All Homelab VPN (WireGuard)
 Configura acesso VPN WireGuard ao homelab RPA4All.
 Inclui configuração automática, DDNS update do endpoint,
 e proteção de download via Authentik SSO.
 .
 Serviços acessíveis após conexão:
  - Rede LAN 192.168.15.0/24
  - VPN subnet 10.66.66.0/24
  - Pi-hole DNS, Grafana, Nextcloud, OpenWebUI
Homepage: https://auth.rpa4all.com/vpn/
